query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('gis')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('arcgis-10.1',
'arcmap',
'arcobjects',
'geoserver',
'openlayers-2',
'openstreetmap',
'polygon',
'python',
'r',
'wms');
